{"tid":1149802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"引渡惡法殺到，香港大團結， 點解方向報與毓民係例外?","createTime":"2019-05-11T11:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T06:13:48.000Z","uid":134071,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd938df7944ee88228295af79d6b89cd783a6d2","tid":1149802,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:41:22.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例修訂， 令非建制派大團結， 熱狗跟泛民破天荒合作拉布。好多本土派中人都讚熱狗同泛民。<br />\n<br />\n除左蘋果日報外， 絕大部分主流媒體都質疑逃犯條例修訂， 但文匯報，大公報跟方向報係例外。<br />\n<br />\n方向報日日出偏頗性報導同評論文章去力撐逃犯條例修訂（甚至暗示希望用逃犯條例去整治反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。）<br />\n而毓民則繼續三分屌建制七分屌飯民 ，最慘係毓民屌飯民既points，係間接俾左位建制派入（例如話涂謹申係向美國佬交差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<br />\n<br />\n係而家既大團結環境下， 點解方向報與毓民會繼續特立獨行？（星島呢d親共報都質疑逃犯條例修訂， 但方向報竟然繼續力撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"0d0968af3f21bbb49d74d22ecbcc878691165048","tid":1149802,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"毓民算唔算養咗班連登狗咬返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2194188320da667b0b4cf852183ea8300733a1b5","tid":1149802,"uid":46896,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0d0968af3f21bbb49d74d22ecbcc878691165048","tid":1149802,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"毓民算唔算養咗班連登狗咬返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"唔通每次有意見唔同就係反骨? 咁嘅話唔怪之得咁多人&ldquo;反骨&rdquo;"},{"pid":"fb8081f772056d68d62137dd5f51b345b1837204","tid":1149802,"uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0d0968af3f21bbb49d74d22ecbcc878691165048","tid":1149802,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"毓民算唔算養咗班連登狗咬返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201